      <title>选举结果令国际货币基金组织贷款面临风险，斯里兰卡债券价格下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/sri-lanka-bonds-tumble-as-leftist-candidate-wins-presidency</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于左翼候选人阿努拉·库马拉·迪萨纳亚克在总统大选中获胜，斯里兰卡获得国际货币基金组织的救助和债务交易面临危险，斯里兰卡的美元债券价格下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/sri-lanka-bonds-tumble-as-leftist-candidate-wins-presidency</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 00:58:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中东冲突和中国刺激计划希望推动油价延续涨势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-september-23</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受中国将加大对中国经济的支持力度以及对以色列和真主党之间冲突可能演变为地区战争的担忧推动，油价在创下 4 月份以来最大单周涨幅后上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-september-23</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 23:32:49 GMT</pubDate>
